Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: S3FileField
Version: 1.0.0
Summary: Specify which fields are an S3 field rather than default to all.
Home-page: http://www.propelmarketing.com
Author: Tyrel Souza
Author-email: tsouza@propelmarketing.com
License: LICENSE.txt
Description: ## This is a Django FileField model field with custom S3 Attributes.
        ### How To Use
        #### Example Model File
            from django.db import models
            from s3filefield.fields import S3FileField
            from s3filefield.signals import s3_clean_model
        
        
            class Resume(models.Model):
                name = models.CharField(max_length=256)
                product = models.CharField(max_length=256)
                pdf = S3FileField(s3_fields=['name', 'product'])
        
        
        #### Example Model File With Cleanup Signal
            from django.db import models
            from s3filefield.fields import S3FileField
            from s3filefield.signals import s3_clean_model
            from django.db.models.signals import pre_delete
        
        
            class Resume(models.Model):
                name = models.CharField(max_length=256)
                product = models.CharField(max_length=256)
                pdf = S3FileField(s3_fields=['name', 'product'])
        
            pre_delete.connect(s3_clean_model, sender=Resume)
        
        
        To install with pip:
            pip install -e git+git@github.com:propelmarketing/s3filefield.git@egg#egg=S3FileField
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
